OL,3,CMP writes to the chancellor to
OL,4,Cformally resign
OL,6,FRuncorn and Helsby MP Mike Amesbury
OL,7,Fhas formally tendered his resignation
OL,8,Fto Chancellor Rachel Reeves after
OL,9,Fbeing handed a suspended prison
OL,10,Fsentence for punching a man in the
OL,11,Fstreet.
OL,13,FMr Amesbury pleaded guilty in January
OL,14,Fto assaulting constituent Paul
OL,15,FFellows, 45, in Frodsham, Cheshire in
OL,16,Fthe early hours of 26 October 2024 and
OL,17,Fwas handed a ten week prison term. His
OL,18,Fsentence was upheld but suspended on
OL,19,Fappeal after he had served three days
OL,20,Fin prison.
