OL,6,FHe was also ordered to carry out 200
OL,7,Fhours of unpaid work, undertake a 120-
OL,8,Fday alcohol monitoring requirement, go
OL,9,Fon an anger management course and
OL,10,Fcomplete 20 days of rehabilitation
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FThe former Labour MP has been sitting
OL,14,Fas an independent since he was
OL,15,Fsuspended by the party after his
OL,16,Farrest last year.
OL,18,FIn a resignation letter to the
OL,19,Fchancellor he wrote:
