OL,3,CMP writes to the chancellor to
OL,4,Cformally resign
OL,6,F"It is with a heavy heart that I write
OL,7,Fto inform you of my decision to resign
OL,8,Ffrom the House of Commons by accepting
OL,9,Fan office under the Crown,"
OL,11,F"This step, though immensely
OL,12,Fdifficult, is the honourable course of
OL,13,Faction that I believe is in the best
OL,14,Finterests of my constituents` whom I
OL,15,Fhave been proud to represent
OL,16,Fthroughout my tenure."
