OL,3,CMP writes to the chancellor to
OL,4,Cformally resign
OL,6,FAmesbury acknowledged that his time as
OL,7,Fan MP "has been curtailed by a mistake
OL,8,Ffor which I have taken full
OL,9,Fresponsibility, both before the
OL,10,Fjudiciary and now in this chamber".
OL,12,F"I offer my sincerest apologies to Mr
OL,13,FFellows, his family, my own family, my
OL,14,Fconstituents, and to Parliament as a
OL,15,Fwhole"
OL,17,FHe won his seat last year with a
OL,18,Fmajority of 14,696 over Reform UK, and
OL,19,Fhis resignation will be a first by-
OL,20,Felection test for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,21,FLabour Party.
